WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.640
Okay, team, we need better ways to be aligned.

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:06.080
We need a two-week sprint rhythm with daily visibility.

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:09.060
It's the only way to stay aligned.

00:00:09.560 --> 00:00:12.040
Daily stand-ups waste engineering time.

00:00:13.260 --> 00:00:16.440
We need deep work blocks and structured milestone reviews.

00:00:16.980 --> 00:00:20.620
Deep work doesn't help if priorities shift and no one sees it.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:24.220
And constant check-ins don't help if people stop building.
